data.description: LOOKING FOR PRIVACY? This beautiful home is nestled on 6-WOODED ACRES centrally located between Wimberley and San Marcos! With 3 bedrooms, 2-1/2 baths plus a study, the open layout invites the relaxed hill country lifestyle you've been waiting for! Easy care stained concrete floors throughout, plus an open and inviting kitchen with high-end appliance package (Bosch dishwasher and Bertazzoni gas range), sure to appeal to the chef in the house! Upgrades include CAT 5 throughout, USB charging ports under kitchen cabinets, and equipped with 110 VAC available at side of house. Currently used as a short-term rental, this property offers many options as a weekend retreat, full-time residence or income producing investment. Minutes to San Marcos and Wimberley shopping, restaurants, and events. SMCISD schools.
